Sunday bakes: Pineapple Tarts.  Sadly, I am only able to get about 60 pieces of this. I don’t have time to get more pineapples or make more of this now. It’s tiring. I wish I had the original crimper for the tarts so can sepit nicely. Also, this won’t last. Sense of smell seeking hidden pineapple tarts in this house is remarkable. I think I’ll just make one more kueh and I’m done. Maybe...
@amy_toi u are such a domestic goddess. ❤️ I can almost imagine  the smell of the tarts lingering in the hse. So nice.
@thebjournal_ 💕thank you. I’m still working on being a perfect one 😂
I’m happy for you. Perfect pineapple 🍍 tart. 👍👍
Wow yum looks gd the shape all 👏👏 yes tarts are tiring esp when u cut n stir yr own pineapple. Great hv a gd rest. Nice for yr tea break tom
U are multi task from sew,cooking n baking amy👏👏👏
